**What type of PR is this?** /kind failing-test **What this PR does / why we need it**: This PR is addressing a panic while running the e2e tests for vsphere cloud provider. The method - `disksAreAttached` is returning a nil map and hence the vsphere cloud provider performance tests are failing. With this fix the test cases are running with no failures. **Which issue(s) this PR fixes**: Fixes #92804 **Special notes for your reviewer**: **Test log before this change:**
